    "name": "Apigee X / GCP Hybrid Management API",
    "description": "The Apigee X and Hybrid Management API (apigee.googleapis.com) provides\nprogrammatic access to Apigee resources deployed on Google Cloud Platform.\nThis includes API proxies, shared flows, environments, environment groups,\ndevelopers, apps, API products, deployments, analytics, debug sessions,\ninstances (hybrid), and more.\n\nBase URL: https://apigee.googleapis.com/v1\n\n**Authentication:** Google OAuth 2.0 or Service Account credentials.\nAll requests require an `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header obtained\nvia Google Cloud credentials.\n\n**Resource naming:** All resources follow the GCP resource naming convention:\n`projects/{project}/...` or `organizations/{org}/...`\n\n**IAM:** Access is controlled by Google Cloud IAM roles such as\n`roles/apigee.admin`, `roles/apigee.apiAdminV2`, `roles/apigee.viewer`.\n",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
